400
00:18:58,163 --> 00:18:59,884
You learned that in high school?

401
00:19:00,323 --> 00:19:01,884
You're way too competitive.

402
00:19:02,403 --> 00:19:03,403
I learned it

403
00:19:04,283 --> 00:19:05,483
