498
00:22:56,163 --> 00:22:56,844
I swear.

499
00:22:56,844 --> 00:22:57,804
If I break my promise...

500
00:22:57,804 --> 00:22:58,392
Enough.

501
00:22:58,524 --> 00:22:59,524
Next time, no mercy.

502
00:23:02,644 --> 00:23:04,764
